The StatsD wire format was originally defined by Etsy:

  StatsD     — https://github.com/statsd/statsd     (MIT)

The DogStatsD dialect (tags, histogram, distribution, service checks,
events) is documented by Datadog:

  https://docs.datadoghq.com/developers/dogstatsd/

The Swift implementation is original; no Etsy or Datadog source is included.

This product depends on swift-bytes (https://github.com/bare-swift/swift-bytes,
Apache-2.0 with LLVM exception) for its Bytes output type.
